                            <b>Bestower Foundation currently offers the following grants:</b><br />

<br />
<b>1. Grants for "The Patient Person of the Year":</b><br />
Every year Bestower Foundation, Lord willing, gives “The Patient Person of the Year“ grant to at least one exemplary patient servant from Bangladesh during the month of Ramadhan, preferably on 27thRamadan. Goal is simple – collect Zakat-ul-fitr and give to the servant who is in tremendous hardship, hoping with Lord's favor, this grant will contribute changing his/her life towards eliminating hardship and attaining goodness.
<br><br />
If you know any person (anywhere in Bangladesh) whose monthly income is less than TK 6000 (equivalent to $78) and has never own TK 6000 in one time, but still very satisfied and grateful to the Lord of the worlds (Exalted is He), please help us to present your nominee by submitting the <a href="./LIB/Forms/Nomination_Form_Patient_Person_of_The_Year_Grant.pdf">nomination form</a> to Bestower Foundation via email at <a href="mailto:grant@bestower.org">grant@bestower.org</a> no later than 10th Ramadan.
The minimum amount for said grant will be, Lord willing, at least TK 100,000 (1 Lac).<br />
<a href="./LIB/Forms/Nomination_Form_Patient_Person_of_The_Year_Grant.pdf"><img src="LIB/Images/pdf.gif" height="10" />Nomination Form for "Patient Person of The Year" Grant</a>

<br /><br />
                            
<br />
<b>2. Ramadan Grants:</b><br />
Every year Bestower Foundation, Lord willing, will give at least one person or family a “Ramadan Grant” for the purpose of  i) providing food for whole month of Ramadan so that said person or family can fast comfortably; and ii) providing EID gift (e.g. clothes) for said person or family.
<br><br />
If you know any person (anywhere in Bangladesh) who is unprivileged and conscious of Allah(swt), please help us to present your nominee by submitting the <a href="./LIB/Forms/Nomination_Form_Ramadan_Grant.pdf">nomination form</a> to Bestower Foundation via email at <a href="mailto:grant@bestower.org">grant@bestower.org</a> at least a week before the month of Ramadan begins.
<br />
<a href="./LIB/Forms/Nomination_Form_Ramadan_Grant.pdf"><img src="LIB/Images/pdf.gif" height="10" />Nomination Form for "Ramadan Grant”</a>

<br /><br />
                            
<br />

<b>3. Grants for the Unprivileged:</b><br />
If you are an unprivileged individual who needs financial assistance to make living, you may download the following application form and submit to Bestower Foundation at <a href="mailto:grant@bestower.org">grant@bestower.org</a>.
<br />
<a href="./LIB/Forms/GrantApplication_for_Unprivileged.pdf"><img src="LIB/Images/pdf.gif" height="10" />Grant Applicaiton for Unprivileged</a>
<br /><br /><br />
<b>4. Grants for Religious Institution:</b><br />
If you are a religious institution and seeking for a grant, you may download the following application form and submit to Bestower Foundation at <a href="mailto:grant@bestower.org">grant@bestower.org</a>.
<br />
<a href="./LIB/Forms/GrantApplication_for_Religious_Institution.pdf"><img src="LIB/Images/pdf.gif" height="10" />Grants Applicaiton for Religious Institution</a>


<br /><br /><br />
<b>5. Grants for Charitable or Educational Institution:</b><br />
If you are a charitable or educational institution and seeking for a grant, you may download the following application form and submit to Bestower Foundation at <a href="mailto:grant@bestower.org">grant@bestower.org</a>.
<br />
<a href="./LIB/Forms/GrantApplication_for_Institution.pdf"><img src="LIB/Images/pdf.gif" height="10" />Grants Applicaiton for Educational/Charitable Institution</a>

<br /><br /><br />
<b>6. Medical Grants for the Unprivileged:</b><br />
If you are an unprivileged individual who needs financial assistance to pay for currently prescribed medications and/or visiting doctors, you may download the following application form and submit to Bestower Foundation at <a href="mailto:grant@bestower.org">grant@bestower.org</a> along with i) <u>picture of the applicant</u>; and ii) <u>picture of the house the applicant currently lives in</u>.
<br />
<a href="./LIB/Forms/MedicalGrantApplication_for_Unprivileged.pdf"><img src="LIB/Images/pdf.gif" height="10" />Medical Grant Applicaiton for Unprivileged</a>

<br /><br />
<b>The application process is open annually from September 1 through December 25 except "Ramadan Grant" and "Patient Person of the Year Grant" which are processed before or during the month of Ramadan.</b> If you are interested in applying for a grant through the Bestower Foundation, please download the apprpriate grant application form (see above) and send the completed applicaiton form to Bestower Foundation at <a href="mailto:grant@bestower.org">grant@bestower.org</a>. 
<br /><br />Consideration will be afforded to all eligible candidates who apply, provided the candidate submits a completed application with all necessary documentation prior to said deadline. 
<br /><br />
Good luck to all of our applicants!

